rows.label: qev085205_MSG0001
rows.name:
Wow, I... Uh...
You really saved our bacon there. Thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0002
rows.name:
It's fine. Situations like this
are exactly what we're here for, after all. [ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0003
rows.name:
But you two better train harder, or you're gonna
keep running into trouble everywhere you go here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0004
rows.name: Yeah, no...you're right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0005
rows.name:
Hey, about the other day? I'm sorry.
We didn't mean anything by it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0006
rows.name: I said it's fine already. Just get home in one piece.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0007
rows.name: R-right![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0008
rows.name: Ugh, it's almost worse when they apologize.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0009
rows.name: Yeah, well, I'm sorry, too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0010
rows.name: Hmm? What for?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0011
rows.name: When I, you know, hesitated to help them out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0012
rows.name:
Oh, that? No worries.
Honestly, I was thinking the same thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0013
rows.name: What? You were?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0014
rows.name:
Sure I was. A jerk is still a jerk,
even if it's your job to save 'em.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0015
rows.name: Harsh, but fair.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0016
rows.name: I still can't believe how quick you jumped in to help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0017
rows.name: Well, we're the only humans on this rock, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0018
rows.name: Our future depends on all of us. Even the dirtbags.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0019
rows.name: If you look at it that way, it was a pretty easy decision.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0020
rows.name: Anyway, thanks, Colonel. My head feels a lot clearer now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0021
rows.name: I appreciate you letting me tag along.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0022
rows.name: Anytime, soldier.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085205_MSG0023
rows.name: All right, let's get back to New LA.[ST:wait ]
